# AT400 GNSS Antenna for RTK

## 1. Application

AT400 is a professional antenna specifically designed for high-precision RTK applications such as surveying and mapping, precision agriculture, robotics, and machine control. It features a stable and reliable carrier phase center, a 150mm ground plane, and can stably receive almost all GNSS frequencies and signals.
